---
title: Taverna Steak & Feta Salad Elevated Dinners, Impressively Easy
description: Evoking the casual elegance of Greek cuisine, this super-quick and hearty dish features tender sliced steak over a fresh and flavorful salad of briny feta cheese, juicy tomatoes, crunchy cucumber, and crisp lettuce. A creamy Greek vinaigrette brings it all together while a side of warm pita bread helps soak up all the flavors.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6655efc38a4eed4f27b52f39-5b84dad6.jpeg
